\description{
For successive inter-spike intervals (ISIs) \eqn{\Delta_i}, the local
Shinomoto LV values are
\deqn{ LV_i = 3 \frac{(\Delta_i - \Delta_{i+1})^2}{(\Delta_i + \Delta_{i+1})^2}. }
